<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA37">
<l>matiyā vaṭalavuṇar māmatiṉmūṉ ṟaṭṭa</l>
<l>matiyār vaḷarcaṭaiyi ṉāṉai - matiyālē</l>
<l>yeṉpākkai yālikaḻā tēttuvarē livvulaki</l>
<l>leṉpākkai yāyppiṟavā rīṇṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If, without despising [his] bone[-adorned] body, they praise</l>
<l>with [their] minds him with matted hair in which the moon grows</l>
<l>who killed the three great fortresses of the unthinking murderous Asuras,</l>
<l>they will not be born [again] here as bodies with bones.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
